50|$|Haato & co. (formerly Gelato di Crema) is a {{retailer}} of dessert based in Singapore, operating {{a chain of}} cafes, and run by the Dessert Empire Private Limited. A Haato cafe is run either by a franchisee or the corporation itself. Haato primarily sells gelato, <b>yoghurt,</b> <b>sorbet,</b> waffles, pastries, beverages and hot food. As of 2011, there are seven Haato outlets across Singapore.|$|E

